ight aligned image and settle in nicely. There should still be plenty of room and everything should be sitting pretty. Yeah... Just like that. It never felt so good to be right. And that''s a wrap, yo! You survived the tumultuous waters of alignment. Image alignment achievement unlocked![/pt_text][pt_image div_margin_top="" div_margin_bottom="" disabled="no" el_title="Image 1" image_file="" image_size="" image_alt="" link_type="no_link" image_image_size="" image_type_url="http://" open_in="current_browser" image_container_style="no-styling" image_alignment="inherit" image_margin="" image_margin_top="" image_margin_right="" image_margin_bottom="" image_margin_left="" image_effect="no" div_margin="" ][/pt_image][/pt_column][/pt_row]\n', 'Image Alignment', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '903-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-04-24 07:18:32', '2014-04-24 07:18:32', '', 903, 'http://borealpaddle/?p=1267', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
